    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hindu and Buddhist prayers, religious consecrations, or initiation rituals. Examples include where an individual is sprinkled with water or other liquid; may symbolize a change in status.</Note_Text>
